                            <textarea id="diagnosis" name="diagnosis" rows="3" placeholder="‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏¥‡∏à‡∏â‡∏±‡∏¢..." required></textarea>
