                            <textarea id="treatmentNotes" name="treatmentNotes" rows="4" placeholder="‡∏Ç‡∏±‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏ï‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏£‡∏±‡∏Å‡∏©‡∏≤, ‡πÄ‡∏ó‡∏Ñ‡∏ô‡∏¥‡∏Ñ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ..."></textarea>
